metadata.name: SYNTH CREEPTH #1
metadata.description: One day while the creepths were scavenging for food, they came across a mysterious portal where they saw a strange version of themselves… Intrigued, the Creepths jumped in and became something new! Creepthereum and Cyber Ocelot present: Synthetically Engineered Creepths! Artificial intelligence has come to creepthereum…
